<A HREF="main.phtml"><B>Polls:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
Well, I let this poll run a little longer then usual as I haven't had much time to work on the site lately, so we got plenty of responses! 1416 people responded and it was a fairly even spread across the choices. The majority of players have played for more then a year (26.41%) which really shows how the game is maturing, yet there are also a lot of mid and low time players. With even 10.24% of players in their first month, that shows that the Scars of Velious has most likely attracted a lot of new customers. Here are the complete results of the poll question <I>"How long have you been playing EverQuest for?"</I></FONT><BR><BR>

<TABLE BORDER=2>
<FONT FACE="verdana, arial" SIZE="1" COLOR="#FFFDCA">
