<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
<P>Our new poll question is "If there are no more add-ons to EQ, about how much longer will you play it?".
</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="maps.php3"><B>Maps:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
Eight new maps added today. As well, I finally got the <A HREF="maps.php3">main maps page</A> changed to show the continent of Velious and the new <A HREF="planes_zones.phtml">Alternate Planes</A>, so that you can search for maps by clicking on the images just like the other continents.</FONT><BR><BR>

<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">1. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Crystal%20Caverns">Crystal Caverns</A> - 3 maps by EQ Atlas</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">2. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Wakening%20lands">Wakening Lands</A> - by EQ Atlas</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">3. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Plane%20of%20Sky">Plane of Sky</A> - by EQgeograf</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">4. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Plane%20of%20Growth">Plane of Growth</A> - by EQgeograf</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">5. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Dragon%20Necropolis">Dragon Necropolis</A> - by EQgeograf</FONT><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">6. <A HREF="map_search.php3?action=zone&add_zone=Tower%20of%20Frozen%20Shadow">Tower of Frozen Shadow</A> - By EQgeograf</FONT><BR><BR>

<A HREF="mailto:webmaster@loreseekers.com?subject=spell%20help"><B>Help Needed!:</B></A><BR>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="arial">
Are you a high level player? Near the upper levels of your particular class? If so, and if you can spare a little free time, then we need your help to finish up our spell database!<BR><BR>

We are looking for volunteers who can take one class and fill in the spell information for that class, to as high a level as they can. We are not looking for just the raw data, but also stratagies and notes about each spell that comes from your experience. So if you would like to help us in this, please email us <A HREF="mailto:webmaster@loreseekers.com?subject=spell%20help">here</A>. Anyone who can help will be given credit on the news and the spell pages. Thanks!</FONT><BR><BR> 

<B><I>MadWand</I></B></FONT></TD></TR></TABLE>	
